mods.abstract: Two color window card (dark brown and light brown on white) announcing Jesse Dayton's Hey Nashvegas! 2001 tour. The poster features a blank space for handwritten tour dates and locations, as well as a woodcut of the artist's initials surrounded by stars and wavy lines.
